"{\"uid\": \"breitbart.com-sports-2024-08-07-exiled-paraguayan-olympic-swimmer-luana-alonso-hints-at-surprising-career-change\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"After being unceremoniously kicked out of the Paris Olympics for \\\"skimpy\\\" attire and \\\"inappropriate behavior,\\\" Paraguayan swimmer Luana Alonso is now hinting at a surprising possible career change.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 197, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 111, \"end\": 121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"score\": 0.9579268422555453, \"rank\": 0.0438944055963259, \"text\": \"Paraguayan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\"}, {\"begin\": 130, \"end\": 135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luana,_Iowa\", \"score\": 0.8124999943797706, \"rank\": 0.23076923076925165, \"text\": \"Luana\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luana,_Iowa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luana,_Iowa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alonso had already been ruled out of the Olympics when she failed to advance to the semifinals in the 100m women's butterfly in July.\", \"from\": 199, \"to\": 332, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, she opted to stay in Paris as the international games progressed instead of returning home to Paraguay.\", \"from\": 333, \"to\": 443, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 361, \"end\": 366, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999304148985526, \"rank\": 6.958994378470282e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 434, \"end\": 442, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"score\": 0.9542501086724845, \"rank\": 0.04791275665908145, \"text\": \"Paraguay\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's when her country's Olympic officials got fed up.\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 503, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paraguayan officialsbrandedher a menace for causing disruptions in their athlete quarters in the Olympic Village and on Monday announced that she had been kicked out of the area.\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 683, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 505, \"end\": 515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"score\": 0.9579268422555453, \"rank\": 0.0438944055963259, \"text\": \"Paraguayan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\"}, {\"begin\": 602, \"end\": 617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999954125940523, \"rank\": 4.587316027440936e-06, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alonso, though,refutedthat characterization and has been wholly unbothered by accusations that she was a \\\"distraction\\\" for her fellow athletes.\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 827, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alonso fully refuted the claims she was a distraction for her fellow athletes.\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 907, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just wanted to make it clear that I was never removed or expelled from anywhere; stop spreading false information,\\\" Alonsowrote, according to theNew York Post.\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 1071, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not want to give any statement but I am not going to let lies affect me either,\\\" she exclaimed.\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1174, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Luana Alonso (@luanalonsom)  Now she is hinting that she just might target the Miss Universe Pageant for her next move.\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1314, \"entities\": [{\"be